'''Nest Leader''' was a position of leadership among the [[Arcona/Legends|Arcona]]<ref name="GG4">[[Galaxy Guide 4: Alien Races (Second Edition)|''Galaxy Guide 4: Alien Races'', Second Edition]]</ref> and the [[Geelan]].<ref name="Journal13">{{JournalCite|13|Alien Encounters (article series)}}</ref> On [[Cona/Legends|Cona]], the elected leader of a [[Grand Nest]] held the title of Nest Leader. The Nest Leader conducted meetings and handled city affairs, much like a [[Mayor/Legends|mayor]].<ref name="GG4" /> In Geelan society, the Nest Leader was elected from a group of Geelans and reported directly to the [[Great Geel]].<ref name="Journal13" />

